Name: The Rodinia Project
About the game: The Rodinia Project is a tranquil first-person sci-fi puzzle adventure. You find yourself in front of a huge structure surrounded by the ocean, alone. Manipulate the environment and overcome challenges consisting of 50 self-contained puzzles to ascend the Nexus and discover the mysteries of these strange installations.
